                                                              |  // [924]
        Call[ THE_HUNK ]and[ THE_HUNK ]will take care of      |  // [924]
        you. The hunk will split you in two. Or maybe         |  // [924]
        three chunks. Or maybe even 13 maximum if you         |  // [924]
        get very unlucky.                                     |  // [924]
                                                              |  // [924]
        But for real, we need to chunk our explosion into     |  // [924]
        up to FOUR sub-explosion rectangles so that           |  // [924]
        we can straddle the boarders of the rooms             |  // [924]
        within the hotel without corrupting data.             |  // [924]
                                                              |  // [924]
