        Going to be a lot of calculations...                  |  // [924]
                                                              |  // [924]
        So... we should DIRECTLY_CALL :                       |  // [924]
                                                              |  // [924]
        [ F_BOMSIMP_EFC_AIB_R13_X64_Y64_DPI_V16 ]             |  // [924]
                                                              |  // [924]
        If we realize the explosion is 100% in bound.         |  // [924]
