        hunker is and is not used by emitting explosions      |  // [924]
        that we know are within the bounds of the             |  // [924]
        current level, the emit explosions                    |  // [924]
        STRADDLING_TWO_OR_MORE_LEVELS and see                 |  // [924]
        if it behaves correctly.                              |  // [924]
